ipmaker over the summer, originally on the back of what the street thought was</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1729780233/image_1729780233.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742710-intel-should-have-kept-gelsinger-rating-downgrade", "pub_date": "2024-12-07 01:05:41"}, {"id": "4742000", "title": "NewLake Capital's Inherent Undervaluation Offers Opportunistic Investors With Rich Returns", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455774438/image_1455774438.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"A US Dollar symbol made of wood with leaves growing from it.\" data-id=\"1455774438\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455774438/image_1455774438.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455774438/image_1455774438.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455774438/image_1455774438.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455774438/image_1455774438.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455774438/image_1455774438.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455774438/image_1455774438.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455774438/image_1455774438.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455774438/image_1455774438.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Richard Drury</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2><strong>NLCP Is Inherently Undervalued - Offering Opportunistic Investors With The Dual Pronged Returns</strong></h2> <p>We previously covered <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4715636-newlake-capital-lock-in-yields-cannabis-federal-rescheduling-near\">NewLake Capital Partners</a> (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/NLCP\" title=\"NewLake Capital Partners, Inc.\">OTCQX:NLCP</a>) in August 2024, discussing its outperformance through the robust FQ2'24 performance metrics as its tenants' profitability continued to</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455774438/image_1455774438.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742000-newlake-capitals-inherent-undervaluation-offers-opportunistic-investors-with-rich-returns", "pub_date": "2024-12-07 00:00:00"}, {"id": "4742706", "title": "Hormel: Q4 Earnings Confirm It's Better To Own The Retailer Than The Brand (Downgrade)", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/482142025/image_482142025.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Full shopping cart in supermarket aisle\" data-id=\"482142025\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1022px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/482142025/image_482142025.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/482142025/image_482142025.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/482142025/image_482142025.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/482142025/image_482142025.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/482142025/image_482142025.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/482142025/image_482142025.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/482142025/image_482142025.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/482142025/image_482142025.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Jacobs Stock Photography Ltd</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Overview</h2> <p>I <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4678071-hormel-stock-mixed-outlook-for-this-dividend-king\">previously covered</a> Hormel Foods (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/HRL\" title=\"Hormel Foods Corporation\">HRL</a></span>) during the first quarter of 2024 and issued a hold rating due to the shift in consumer spending towards store-branded items. A driver of the lackluster sales</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/482142025/image_482142025.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742706-hormel-q4-earnings-better-to-own-the-retailer-than-the-brand", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 23:49:05"}, {"id": "4742704", "title": "FitLife Brands: Q3 Results Weren't As Bad As They Seem - Still A Buy", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/619091536/image_619091536.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Scoop of whey protein on black background. Chocolate flawour\" data-id=\"619091536\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1017px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/619091536/image_619091536.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/619091536/image_619091536.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekinga