date": "2024-12-06 23:05:04"}, {"id": "4742705", "title": "Is Market Optimism Outpacing Realistic Growth Potential?", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1397937755/image_1397937755.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Financial asset invest analysis with volume and candle stick chart\" data-id=\"1397937755\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1022px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1397937755/image_1397937755.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1397937755/image_1397937755.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1397937755/image_1397937755.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1397937755/image_1397937755.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1397937755/image_1397937755.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1397937755/image_1397937755.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1397937755/image_1397937755.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1397937755/image_1397937755.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">TERADAT SANTIVIVUT</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Equity markets have spent much of 2024 in record territory. But with a new U.S. president moving into the White House, concerns about current valuations and potential economic headwinds, can that momentum continue? Phil Davis, founder of Philstockworld.com, discusses why he believes recent market</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1397937755/image_1397937755.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742705-market-optimism-outpacing-realistic-growth-potential", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 22:46:00"}, {"id": "4742703", "title": "EUR/USD: Additional Accommodative Monetary Policy Guidance From The ECB May Be Forthcoming", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1126632524/image_1126632524.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Euro currency symbol\" data-id=\"1126632524\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"7952px\" height=\"5304px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1126632524/image_1126632524.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1126632524/image_1126632524.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1126632524/image_1126632524.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1126632524/image_1126632524.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1126632524/image_1126632524.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1126632524/image_1126632524.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1126632524/image_1126632524.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1126632524/image_1126632524.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Daniel Grizelj</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By Kelvin Wong</em></p> <p>For next Thursday, 12 December European Central Bank (ECB) monetary policy outcome, market participants are likely to expect a 25-basis point (BPS) cut rather than a more aggressive reduction of 50 bps based on short-term interest rate futures pricing.</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1126632524/image_1126632524.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742703-eur-usd-additional-accommodative-monetary-policy-guidance-ecb-may-be-forthcoming", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 22:23:00"}, {"id": "4742701", "title": "GraniteShares 2x Long COIN ETF: Fortune Favors The Brave", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1383032511/image_1383032511.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Paying in cyber space\" data-id=\"1383032511\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1266px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1383032511/image_1383032511.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1383032511/image_1383032511.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1383032511/image_1383032511.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1383032511/image_1383032511.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1383032511/image_1383032511.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1383032511/image_1383032511.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1383032511/image_1383032511.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1383032511/image_1383032511.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">PM Images</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>I last covered the <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4717407-graniteshares-2x-long-coin-etf-proof-in-pudding\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4717407-graniteshares-2x-long-coin-etf-proof-in-pudding\" target=\"_blank\">GraniteShares 2x Long COIN Daily ETF</a> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CONL\" title=\"GraniteShares 2x Long COIN Daily ETF\">CONL</a></span>) for Seeking Alpha in late August. For the second time this year, I rated CONL a 'sell' and made the argument that the proof was in the pudding on the fund. At</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1383032511/image_1383032511.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742701-graniteshares-2x-long-coin-etf-fortune-favors-the-brave", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 22:19:26"}, {"id": "4742699", "title": "Zumiez Is Recovering, But The Price Already Discounts A Full Turnaround", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/516750419/image_516750419.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Skateboarder falling off of railing in skate park\" data-id=\"516750419\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/516750419/image_516750419.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/516750419/image_516750419.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/516750419/image_516750419.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/516750419/image_516750419.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekin